Summary: same event that just happened recently in fla.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my apartment on the 7th floor watching tv when my wife noticed something outside in the sky.I got my binoculars an viewed the same type of event that just happened recently in fla.It was three firely balls moving at a fairly smooth pace to the contour of are orbit.They were in plan view with i would say flying no higher then a small plane would.I lost site of the objects due to other buildings in the area.I reported it to the new an the following day someone i worked with asked if i had seen it due to the fact that i had lived in the city.I truely belevie that it came out of hickem air force base.Im not sure if the one in fla. was close to a base.Though if it was i belevie the military has a jet plane that is invisble except for the heat the jet engines let off.After seeing a radar of a jet the fireball looked the same.
